&lt;li&gt;You are confident navigating sales cycles with all management levels (particularly SVP/C-Level)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organization and prioritizing are at the heart of everything you do and you are disciplined and function well in a remote environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What is a salesperson without professional communication skills, and a customer-centric, personable demeanor?!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can balance driving a sales cycle independently while leveraging internal resources&lt;/li&gt;
